{"tid":1109423,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【有圖】杜德偉蔡一智去鯉魚門食海鮮 點解大家咁大反應","createTime":"2019-04-16T09:20:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-16T14:02:47.000Z","uid":242050,"like":16,"dislike":383,"uniUserReply":46,"replies":[{"pid":"e5adce70cb86a1d244eee020bd7e627225fedede","tid":1109423,"uid":242050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T09:20:00.000Z","msg":"今日蘋果報導杜德偉同埋蔡一智去鯉魚門搭的士食海鮮🦞 點解大家咁大反應？你哋係咪唔抵得佢地有得食啊？<br />\n<br />\n鯉魚門啲海鮮真係幾好食㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你哋未食過咩？<br />\n俾啲相你哋睇吓啦<br />\n<br />\n嗰日我係隔離檯食飯，見佢兩個叫咗兩道菜，難得見到明星我梗係走過去同佢地R合照啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我講咗一句：「杜生，可唔可以可以同你影張相？」但佢真人好串，叫佢杜生都唔應我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n佢兩個雖然淨係叫咗「菲律賓黑鮑魚」同埋「淺水灣象拔蚌刺身」不過埋單都好似唔平<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mocZef4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmocZef4.png&h=e66a1d1a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rXHqUf4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrXHqUf4.png&h=08ab8baa&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"63c9ed5db678d52d2707fe753cbfa47c8e6be81f","tid":1109423,"uid":81037,"like":315,"dislike":2,"score":313,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T09:20:55.000Z","msg":"😅..."},{"pid":"97e4d8587610d4748881dc38cd63743d6f8a724d","tid":1109423,"uid":74182,"like":183,"dislike":0,"score":183,"quote":{"pid":"e5adce70cb86a1d244eee020bd7e627225fedede","tid":1109423,"uid":242050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T09:20:00.000Z","msg":"今日蘋果報導杜德偉同埋蔡一智去鯉魚門搭的士食海鮮🦞 點解大家咁大反應？你哋係咪唔抵得佢地有得食啊？<br />\n<br />\n鯉魚門啲海鮮真係幾好食㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" cla